### ==========================================
### VARIÁVEIS — salvas automaticamente pelo script de login
### auth_token  → token do usuário comum
### admin_token → token do admin (se criar um)
### ==========================================


### ==========================================
### 1. AUTH
### ==========================================

### [1.1] Registrar novo usuário (público, sem token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Luiza Dados",
  "email": "luiza@dadosportodos.com",
  "username": "vbluuiza",
  "password": "senhaSegura123"
}

###

### [1.2] Login e salva token automaticamente
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "luiza@dadosportodos.com",
  "password": "senhaSegura123"
}

> {% client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token); %}

###

### [1.3] Tentar registrar com email duplicado → espera 400
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Luiza Duplicada",
  "email": "luiza@dadosportodos.com",
  "username": "vbluuiza2",
  "password": "senhaSegura123"
}

###

### [1.4] Tentar login com senha errada → espera 403
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "luiza@dadosportodos.com",
  "password": "senhaErrada"
}

###

### [1.5] Registrar com body inválido (sem email) → espera 400 com mensagem de validação
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sem Email",
  "username": "semEmail",
  "password": "senhaSegura123"
}

###


### ==========================================
### 2. USUÁRIOS
### ==========================================

### [2.1] Listar usuários sem token → espera 403
GET http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios

###

### [2.2] Listar usuários com token (USER vê PublicUserDTO, ADMIN vê tudo)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### [2.3] Buscar usuário por ID (só ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### [2.4] Atualizar usuário (próprio usuário ou ADMIN)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Luiza Dados Atualizado",
  "email": "luiza@dadosportodos.com",
  "username": "vbluuiza_updated",
  "password": "senhaSegura123"
}

###

### [2.5] Criar usuário via UsuarioController (só ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin Teste",
  "email": "admin@teste.com",
  "username": "admin_teste",
  "password": "adminPass123"
}

###


### ==========================================
### 3. EVENTOS
### ==========================================

### [3.1] Listar todos os eventos (sem token — rota pública)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/eventos

###

### [3.2] Buscar evento por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/eventos/1

###

### [3.3] Criar evento (só ADMIN — se for USER espera 403)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/eventos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "eventName": "Data Engineering Day",
  "description": "Evento sobre engenharia de dados com GCP e BigQuery",
  "capacity": 100,
  "isFree": true,
  "scheduledAt": "2026-10-10T20:00:00",
  "price": 0.0,
  "expectedAttendance": 80,
  "isWeekend": false,
  "category": "CORPORATIVO",
  "eventTypeId": null,
  "creatorId": 1,
  "locationDetail": "Auditório Principal",
  "imageUrl": null
}

###

### [3.4] Criar evento com body inválido → espera 400
POST http://localhost:8080/api/eventos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "eventName": "AB",
  "capacity": -5,
  "price": -10.0
}

###

### [3.5] Criar evento sem token → espera 403
POST http://localhost:8080/api/eventos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventName": "Evento Sem Auth",
  "capacity": 50,
  "isFree": true,
  "scheduledAt": "2026-10-10T20:00:00",
  "price": 0.0,
  "expectedAttendance": 10
}

###


### ==========================================
### 4. INSCRIÇÕES
### ==========================================

### [4.1] Fazer inscrição num evento
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "eventId": 1,
  "visitorCount": 2
}

###

### [4.2] Fazer inscrição sem registrationAt (service preenche com now())
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "eventId": 1,
  "visitorCount": 1
}

###

### [4.3] Tentar inscrição com visitorCount inválido → espera 400
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "eventId": 1,
  "visitorCount": -1
}

###

### [4.4] Tentar inscrição num evento que não existe → espera 404
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "eventId": 9999,
  "visitorCount": 1
}

###

### [4.5] Ver minhas inscrições (filtra pelo token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes/me
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### [4.6] Listar todas as inscrições (só ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###


### ==========================================
### 5. AGENDAMENTOS
### ==========================================

### [5.1] Criar agendamento
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agendamentos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "eventId": 1,
  "personCount": 3
}

###

### [5.2] Criar agendamento com bookedAt explícito
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agendamentos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "eventId": 1,
  "bookedAt": "2026-05-10T14:00:00",
  "personCount": 2
}

###

### [5.3] Criar agendamento com usuário inexistente → espera 404
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agendamentos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": 9999,
  "eventId": 1,
  "personCount": 1
}

###

### [5.4] Listar todos os agendamentos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/agendamentos
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### [5.5] Buscar agendamento por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/agendamentos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### [5.6] Buscar agendamento que não existe → espera 404
GET http://localhost:8080/api/agendamentos/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###


### ==========================================
### 6. VISITAS
### ==========================================

### [6.1] Agendar uma visita (data futura obrigatória)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/visitas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "scheduledAt": "2026-12-01T10:00:00",
  "requesterId": 1,
  "authorizerId": null
}

###

### [6.2] Agendar visita com data no passado → espera 400
POST http://localhost:8080/api/visitas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "scheduledAt": "2020-01-01T10:00:00",
  "requesterId": 1
}

###

### [6.3] Agendar visita sem requesterId → espera 400
POST http://localhost:8080/api/visitas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "scheduledAt": "2026-12-01T10:00:00"
}

###

### [6.4] Listar todas as visitas
GET http://localhost:8080/api/visitas
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### [6.5] Buscar visita por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/visitas/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###


### ==========================================
### 7. SUGESTÕES
### ==========================================

### [7.1] Enviar sugestão (creator vem do token, não do body)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sugestoes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "eventName": "Trilha de Cloud Data",
  "description": "Adicionar trilha de Cloud Data com GCP no próximo evento DPT",
  "category": "CORPORATIVO"
}

###

### [7.2] Enviar sugestão sem token → espera 403
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sugestoes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventName": "Trilha sem auth",
  "description": "Não deve funcionar"
}

###

### [7.3] Enviar sugestão com nome curto → espera 400
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sugestoes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "eventName": "AB",
  "description": "Nome muito curto"
}

###

### [7.4] Listar todas as sugestões
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sugestoes
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### [7.5] Buscar sugestão por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sugestoes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### [7.6] Buscar sugestão que não existe → espera 404
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sugestoes/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###
